inical handovers in the real world of practice.' -Professor Suzanne Kurtz, Washington State University 'This clear, plain English book is an outstanding resource for the training of all involved in healthcare.' -Elizabeth Trickett, (Former) Director of Safety and Quality, ACT Health, Australia  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 30. Aug 2021) 4aClinical handoff. 4aClinical handover. 4ahospital communication. 4amedical communication. 4anursing communication. 7aMEDICAL / Clinical Medicine.2bisacsh1 aBear, Jacqui, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBear, Jacqui.1 aCominos, Nayia, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCominos, Nayia.1 aDella, Phillip, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDella, Phillip.1 aEggins, Suzanne, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aEggins, Suzanne, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aGeddes, Fiona , eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aGeddes, Fiona, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aJones, Dorothy, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aJones, Dorothy.1 aJureidini, Jon, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aJureidini, Jon.1 aLee, Marian, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLee, Marian.1 aManias, Elizabeth, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aManias, Elizabeth.1 aMcGregor, Jeannette, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMcGregor, Jeannette.1 aPirone, Christy, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPirone, Christy.1 aPlebani, Mario.1 aSlade, Diana, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/r